roup of skilled managers and directors who work for various businesses, industries and organizations. They help the college with many of its programs, recruiting efforts and fundraising activities. They also serve as a liaison between the college and outside organizations. College Advisory Board 2016-2017 Joshua B. Ballard Zyvex Labs Craig Berry Siemens PLM Software, Inc. Rick Beutter Stryker Communications Don Burgio Verizon Charles Campbell Labinal Jason Cinek* TDIndustries Larry Eckersley Freese and Nichols Inc. Kris Fitzgerald NTT Data Jeremy Green Zodiac Aerospace Lettie K. Haynes* BNSF Railway Company Aaron Howard* PDX Alessia Moscatelli British Telecom, Amaericas Scott Newhouse Peterbilt Motors Co. Lee Palmer* Hitachi Consulting Ray Pahler Encore Wire Chris Pearce* Cisco Systems John Randall Zyvex Labs H. Keith Seawright L-3 Communications Michael Severson Bell Helicopter Anthony CK Soong Huawei Paul Strauss Medtronic Andrew Toth Triumph Aerostructures-Vought Commercial Division  *College of Engineering alumni   About Us Accreditation Staff Directory Advisory Board Corporate Partners IT Services About Discovery Park Take a Tour Maps & Directions History of the College Strategic Plan Organizational Chart Alumni Videos Photo Gallery Research Centers Center for Advanced Research and Technology Center for Advanced Scientific Computing and Modeling Center for Computational Epidemiology and Response Analysis Center for Information and Cyber Security Net-Centric Software and Systems Center PACCAR Technology Institute Contact Us: UNT College of Engineering 3940 N Elm Street Denton, TX 76207-7102 USA Voice: 940-565-4300 Fax: 940-369-8570 Visit Us: UNT Discovery Park http://engineering.unt.edu/ Email us: Have questions about website technical issues? Please contact us. Have other questions? Please visit our contact page. UNT System: UNT Home UNT System UNT Dallas UNT Health Science Center Site last updated on May 5, 2017 Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy Statement | We